  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Applicator<Effect,​Model>  
    EffectExpression<Event>
    Declares the ability of an object to be evaluated under any Projection.
    EffectTrait<Effect>
    A trait for performing effect-algebraic operations on a type.
    Projection<Event,​Effect>
    A projection from an EventGraph to some accumulated effect type.

    EffectExpressionDisplay
    A module for representing EffectExpressions in a textual form.
    EventGraph<Event>
